---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About | Pnicta"
			description="Parent company of Antimony Labs and Antimony Home."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main class="container">
			<h1>About Pnicta</h1>

			<p>
				Pnicta exists to organize technically minded companies around a shared
				standard: do the work correctly, document it properly, and eliminate
				unnecessary complexity.
			</p>

			<h2>Structure</h2>
			<p>
				The company currently operates Antimony Labs and Antimony Home,
				each focused on different domains with the same expectation of precision.
			</p>

			<h2>Operating philosophy</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Minimum compliance is not the goal</li>
				<li>Systems reduce noise</li>
				<li>Good work should look clean because it is clean</li>
			</ul>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
.container {
	max-width:900px;
	margin:auto;
	padding:3rem 1rem;
}
</style>
